Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:44.52,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}手を伸ばして　焦がれていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:48.60,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}届くはずない　光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:52.56,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}こんな世界で　こんな世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:55.15,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}何度も見てた夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:06.74,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}君の割れた　硝子細工
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:10.46,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur4}触れた指が　痛いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:14.71,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}大切なもの　要らないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.71,0:01:17.53,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}元には戻せない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:22.39,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愛　一雫　頬を濡らして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:25.31,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}切なく　雨が降る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:30.72,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}まだ何も君を知らないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:34.77,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}その涙が　止まったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:38.57,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}笑ってみてほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:42.91,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}あ憧れて　憧れて　想像を形へと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:46.77,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}変えるリアリティ　空を駆けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:51.05,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}行くよ　窓の外は君を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:52.96,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}連れ出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:55.52,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}真っ暗な雲が去って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:02:00.10,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}残した水面に　映る色は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:06.72,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨上がり　君は　君の目で答えを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:09.85,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}探してほしい
Comment: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:41.48,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,OP-CN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:44.52,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我所伸出的手　如此急不可耐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:48.60,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}那所无法传达　光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:52.56,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}在如此的天地里　在这样的世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:55.15,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}浮生若梦　回眸几何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:06.74,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}你所制作的　玻璃饰品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:10.46,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur4}指尖一触　寸心如割
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:14.71,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}必不可少的　不再所需的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.71,0:01:17.53,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}至始至终　覆水难收
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:22.39,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}爱　仅需一滴　脸颊便能浸润
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:25.31,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}心如刀绞　雨恨云愁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:30.72,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我还是对你　一无所知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:34.77,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那些落泪　就此止泣的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:38.57,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}多想与你　欢声笑语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:42.91,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如此憧憬　如此向往　想象便形成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:46.77,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就能改变当下　于晴空翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:51.05,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一起出发吧　窗外的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:52.96,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}携手与你共赏春秋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:55.52,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}黑云已散　风光日霁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:02:00.10,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨后镜花水月　依旧彩虹色映
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:06.72,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨过天晴的你　眼眸自知物理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:09.85,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不过我想让你　所寻自己而已
